OL,3,CLabour vows to nationalise railways
OL,4,Cwithin five years if it wins election
OL,6,FUnder the plans, fares would be
OL,7,Fsimplified, but the Party could not
OL,8,Fsay if they would be any less
OL,9,Fexpensive, as ITV News Political
OL,10,FCorrespondent Harry Horton explains
