OL,3,CLabour vows to nationalise railways
OL,4,Cwithin five years if it wins election
OL,6,FA Labour government would expect to
OL,7,Ftransfer rail networks to public
OL,8,Fownership within its first term by
OL,9,Ffolding existing private passenger
OL,10,Frail contracts into a new body as they
OL,11,Fexpire, shadow transport secretary
OL,12,FLouise Haigh will say at a launch
OL,13,Fevent on Thursday.
OL,15,FThe plan will nationalise the network
OL,16,F"without the taxpayer paying a penny
OL,17,Fin compensation costs", the party is
OL,18,Fexpected to say.
