OL,6,FThe party also plans to establish a
OL,7,Fwatchdog, the Passenger Standards
OL,8,FAuthority, to hold GBR to account.
OL,10,FITV News Political Correspondent Harry
OL,11,FHorton explains what Labour's policy
OL,12,Fcould mean for passengers
OL,14,F"With Labour's bold reforms, a
OL,15,Fpublicly owned railway will be single-
OL,16,Fmindedly focused on delivering for
OL,17,Fpassengers and will be held to account
OL,18,Fon delivering reliable, safe,
OL,19,Fefficient, accessible, affordable and
OL,20,Fquality services," Ms Haigh will say.
