OL,3,CLabour vows to nationalise railways
OL,4,Cwithin five years if it wins election
OL,6,FThe party also plans to bring in
OL,7,Fautomatic delay and cancellation
OL,8,Frefunds, make digital season tickets
OL,9,Favailable on all networks, and make
OL,10,Ftimetables, tickets and fares more
OL,11,Fintegrated. It also proposes moving
OL,12,Fmobile service on trains towards 5G
OL,13,Fand improving the integration of rail
OL,14,Ftravel with bus and cycle hire
OL,15,Fservices.
OL,17,FThe government's reform plans were
OL,18,Fbased on recommendations from a review
OL,19,Fcarried out by former British Airways
OL,20,Fchief executive Keith Williams.
